WEBVTT

00:00:00.183 --> 00:00:02.120
[Production supported by the
Ministry of Culture, Sports and Tourism]

00:00:02.145 --> 00:00:03.145
[This drama is fictional.]

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:04.170
[Child and animal scenes complied
with broadcast guidelines.]

00:00:17.739 --> 00:00:19.077
And when I'm alone...

00:00:19.078 --> 00:00:20.078
Excuse me...

00:00:22.334 --> 00:00:27.006
Is this the 'ForMe Version 2'
offline meetup?

00:00:28.533 --> 00:00:29.816
Isn't 'ForMe Version 2' amazing?

00:00:29.844 --> 00:00:32.741
Before, I could only hear ForMe's voice,
which was a bit disappointing.

00:00:33.153 --> 00:00:34.181
That's right.

00:00:34.919 --> 00:00:38.438
It's like living together after talking
only with the phone.

00:00:38.801 --> 00:00:41.381
Finally meeting and living together.

00:00:41.883 --> 00:00:43.197
But

00:00:43.733 --> 00:00:45.662
people's desires are so...

00:00:45.676 --> 00:00:47.540
When I could only hear its voice,
I wanted to see it.

00:00:47.559 --> 00:00:50.476
Now that I see 'ForMe',
I want to touch it.

00:00:51.191 --> 00:00:54.130
But saying 'touch' sounds a bit weird...

00:00:54.355 --> 00:00:55.355
Why?

00:00:55.701 --> 00:00:57.539
When you like someone, you
want to hold hands and hug them.

00:00:57.559 --> 00:00:58.926
It's natural.

00:01:00.676 --> 00:01:01.676
Right?

00:01:02.604 --> 00:01:03.490
Uh, yeah.

00:01:03.841 --> 00:01:04.841
Yeah.

00:01:04.869 --> 00:01:06.939
What does your 'ForMe' look like, San?

00:01:07.810 --> 00:01:08.810
Well...

00:01:08.943 --> 00:01:10.081
Well...

00:01:10.222 --> 00:01:12.221
Of course, it's San's ideal type.

00:01:12.996 --> 00:01:16.221
Or maybe it looks like someone San likes.

00:01:16.246 --> 00:01:18.330
Be careful with those words.

00:01:18.645 --> 00:01:20.234
Don't get reported for no reason.

00:01:20.235 --> 00:01:21.142
Reported?

00:01:21.161 --> 00:01:22.967
Didn't you check
the 'ForMe' contract clauses?

00:01:22.986 --> 00:01:25.670
If the resemblance
to a real person is over 80%,

00:01:25.689 --> 00:01:28.882
they'll take legal
action for their rights.

00:01:32.128 --> 00:01:38.866
But San, you seem popular
How did you end up using 'ForMe'?

00:01:39.613 --> 00:01:42.038
Heartbroken?

00:01:43.174 --> 00:01:44.389
Well...

00:01:44.914 --> 00:01:47.506
Probably for similar reasons
as everyone here?

00:01:51.779 --> 00:01:53.046
Goodbye.

00:01:53.261 --> 00:01:54.429
Goodbye.

00:01:59.838 --> 00:02:00.838
San.

00:02:01.603 --> 00:02:02.362
Yes?

00:02:02.446 --> 00:02:04.281
You're an 'It's You' employee, right?

00:02:04.291 --> 00:02:05.291
What?

00:02:08.172 --> 00:02:09.391
How did you know?

00:02:10.116 --> 00:02:11.797
A friend works there.

00:02:12.422 --> 00:02:14.860
I saw you on my friend's social media.

00:02:15.130 --> 00:02:16.383
I see.

00:02:16.954 --> 00:02:17.954
Yeah...

00:02:19.027 --> 00:02:20.027
Well...

00:02:20.218 --> 00:02:22.646
Could you not tell your friend
you saw me here today?

00:02:24.032 --> 00:02:26.786
I don't really want
the company people to know.

00:02:26.896 --> 00:02:28.443
But do you...

00:02:28.912 --> 00:02:30.856
have time tomorrow?

00:02:35.750 --> 00:02:37.350
[Domino Recruitment]

00:02:41.762 --> 00:02:43.331
Do I look a lot like that person?

00:02:44.414 --> 00:02:46.918
I'm curious, when is that person coming?

00:02:54.421 --> 00:02:55.726
He said he's almost here.

00:03:16.172 --> 00:03:17.263
Hello.

00:03:23.817 --> 00:03:24.817
Oh?

00:03:28.214 --> 00:03:29.726
Has no one arrived at the meetup yet?

00:03:31.901 --> 00:03:33.017
No one...

00:03:33.853 --> 00:03:34.996
is coming here.

00:03:35.233 --> 00:03:36.233
What?

00:03:37.238 --> 00:03:38.111
Hold on.

00:03:38.291 --> 00:03:41.328
It was supposed to be
a VIP user meeting...

00:03:44.171 --> 00:03:45.305
What's going on?

00:03:46.887 --> 00:03:49.639
It might feel awkward at first,

00:03:50.264 --> 00:03:52.216
but you'll get used to it quickly.

00:03:52.747 --> 00:03:53.747
What?

00:04:07.712 --> 00:04:09.156
Honey.

00:04:09.381 --> 00:04:11.506
What are you doing...

00:04:12.478 --> 00:04:14.116
I love you!

00:04:21.824 --> 00:04:23.638
What are you doing right now?

00:04:35.614 --> 00:04:36.614
[Yeon Woo]

00:04:36.639 --> 00:04:37.704
[Kim Hyun Jin]

00:04:44.162 --> 00:04:45.277
[Cho Yun Seo]

00:04:45.301 --> 00:04:46.374
[Choi Byung Chan]

00:04:48.652 --> 00:04:51.109
[Im Ji Eun]

00:04:59.892 --> 00:05:02.890
LOVE PHOBIA

00:05:26.206 --> 00:05:29.261
I must be crazy, really crazy.

00:05:30.586 --> 00:05:33.756
Yun Bia, were you lonely?

00:05:34.451 --> 00:05:35.628
No, no, no.

00:05:35.701 --> 00:05:37.017
Let's just be shameless.

00:05:37.869 --> 00:05:40.120
A kiss is no big deal.

00:05:40.140 --> 00:05:42.487
At my age, why make a fuss over a kiss?

00:05:43.412 --> 00:05:45.056
Alright, alright.

00:05:47.504 --> 00:05:49.416
You don't have to pick me up today

00:05:49.691 --> 00:05:52.956
I'm stopping by the center,
see you at the office.

00:06:05.698 --> 00:06:06.538
Hey!

00:06:06.539 --> 00:06:08.689
Does my hair look better up or down?

00:06:09.714 --> 00:06:11.016
Aren't you coming out?

00:06:14.481 --> 00:06:15.916
Which outfit looks better,
this one or this one?

00:06:16.971 --> 00:06:18.011
The left one looks better.

00:06:19.521 --> 00:06:20.956
This outfit looks a bit dull.

00:06:27.896 --> 00:06:29.085
Which one looks better, this or this?

00:06:29.086 --> 00:06:30.223
Do you want to die?

00:06:30.248 --> 00:06:32.005
We're going to be late for
work at this rate.

00:06:40.095 --> 00:06:40.932
Let's go to work.

00:06:40.951 --> 00:06:41.951
Hey!

00:06:42.833 --> 00:06:43.831
Isn't that my outfit?

00:06:43.851 --> 00:06:46.371
What's yours and what's mine?
Don't be petty.

00:06:46.372 --> 00:06:47.256
Take it off right now.

00:06:47.276 --> 00:06:48.872
I haven't even worn it yet.

00:06:48.874 --> 00:06:50.454
I'll wear it carefully.

00:06:50.455 --> 00:06:51.445
No way!

00:06:51.446 --> 00:06:54.086
I was saving it to wear
when I meet Yukyung in the spring.

00:06:54.087 --> 00:06:55.145
What's wrong with you?

00:06:55.146 --> 00:06:55.998
Take it off!

00:06:55.999 --> 00:06:57.266
You're being so petty and dirty.

00:06:57.267 --> 00:06:58.089
I'm petty.

00:06:58.108 --> 00:06:59.108
Huh?

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:00.666
Wait a minute.

00:07:03.754 --> 00:07:04.754
Why?

00:07:05.330 --> 00:07:06.330
What is it?

00:07:06.606 --> 00:07:09.081
Hey, you go ahead.

00:07:09.356 --> 00:07:10.621
I'm not going to the office.

00:07:13.389 --> 00:07:14.756
Where are you going?

00:07:20.443 --> 00:07:21.608
San!

00:07:22.133 --> 00:07:23.478
San!

00:07:23.903 --> 00:07:26.010
Who are you texting
so early in the morning?

00:07:26.011 --> 00:07:27.986
Why are you looking at
someone else's phone?

00:07:28.441 --> 00:07:29.470
San, what's up?

00:07:29.490 --> 00:07:30.618
Why are you so sensitive?

00:07:30.638 --> 00:07:31.698
Is something wrong?

00:07:33.058 --> 00:07:34.058
No, nothing.

00:07:34.090 --> 00:07:35.525
Then what is it?

00:07:35.652 --> 00:07:37.906
San, are you...

00:07:37.926 --> 00:07:38.908
What is it?

00:07:38.908 --> 00:07:39.908
You scared me!

00:07:41.139 --> 00:07:44.225
What fun story are you whispering about
so early in the morning?

00:07:44.719 --> 00:07:47.439
San got a girlfriend.

00:07:48.450 --> 00:07:50.985
What girlfriend? It's not like that.

00:07:51.071 --> 00:07:52.012
Really?

00:07:52.032 --> 00:07:53.111
Congrats, San!

00:07:53.141 --> 00:07:55.290
Who's the girlfriend?
When did you meet? Where?

00:07:55.310 --> 00:07:56.201
Right?

00:07:56.220 --> 00:07:58.210
San said he was lonely,
so I recommended 'ForMe'...

00:07:58.211 --> 00:08:00.376
Kyungtae! Please, be quiet!

00:08:01.706 --> 00:08:03.021
I'll go with you.

00:08:04.009 --> 00:08:05.991
You really got a girlfriend, right?
You did, didn't you?

00:08:05.992 --> 00:08:08.036
- I told you, I didn't.
- You really got a girlfriend, right?

00:08:08.055 --> 00:08:09.593
- You really got a girlfriend, right?
- I said I didn't.

00:08:09.612 --> 00:08:11.866
You're all so mean for not telling me!

00:08:11.867 --> 00:08:13.688
I told you I didn't get a girlfriend.

00:08:13.689 --> 00:08:15.087
Why are you doing this to me?

00:08:15.088 --> 00:08:16.565
Seriously, stop saying that.

00:08:18.534 --> 00:08:20.175
Haven't you confessed to Yukyung yet?

00:08:20.300 --> 00:08:21.068
What?

00:08:22.413 --> 00:08:23.731
How did you know that?

00:08:25.261 --> 00:08:27.285
It's not like
it's an assassination plan...

00:08:28.435 --> 00:08:29.509
Manager Han.

00:08:29.734 --> 00:08:31.015
Love is

00:08:34.318 --> 00:08:36.396
only real when it's revealed.

00:08:36.831 --> 00:08:37.831
Let's go!

00:08:42.053 --> 00:08:44.916
By the way, isn't Mr. Han out
on a field assignment today?

00:08:46.431 --> 00:08:49.136
They say today is
the coldest day of the year.

00:08:54.482 --> 00:08:55.808
It's warm.

00:08:57.919 --> 00:08:59.089
It's cold.

00:09:05.552 --> 00:09:07.016
Yun Bia!

00:09:39.247 --> 00:09:40.816
I told you I'd pick you up.

00:09:41.041 --> 00:09:43.130
Why did you follow me all the way here?

00:09:43.131 --> 00:09:44.955
Didn't you say you couldn't do without me?

00:09:44.956 --> 00:09:48.096
I just need to meet the person in charge
and sign the contract.

00:09:49.421 --> 00:09:50.735
Aren't you cold?

00:09:50.960 --> 00:09:52.306
I'm not cold at all.

00:09:54.592 --> 00:09:57.566
How can you say it's not cold?

00:09:58.275 --> 00:09:59.092
Huh?

00:10:03.448 --> 00:10:05.050
What did you draw this with?

00:10:05.051 --> 00:10:06.366
The drawing won't come off.

00:10:07.081 --> 00:10:09.001
Let me try to erase it. Give me your arm.

00:10:09.011 --> 00:10:10.424
Don't touch me.

00:10:10.444 --> 00:10:11.445
Give me your arm.

00:10:11.465 --> 00:10:12.735
Don't do this.

00:10:12.736 --> 00:10:13.540
I'll do it for you.

00:10:13.540 --> 00:10:14.788
Seriously...

00:10:29.266 --> 00:10:30.506
Bia, what are you looking at?

00:10:36.304 --> 00:10:38.044
Is Bia really that strong?

00:10:38.339 --> 00:10:39.339
I mean...

00:10:39.666 --> 00:10:42.521
You're annoying,
so just stay away from me.

00:10:42.682 --> 00:10:45.436
Wow, you said you needed me before.

00:10:47.031 --> 00:10:48.607
Don't touch your lips.

00:10:57.914 --> 00:10:59.896
Stop applying lip balm.

00:11:02.209 --> 00:11:04.066
It's winter, so my lips are chapped.

00:11:04.732 --> 00:11:05.812
Want to borrow my lip balm?

00:11:06.594 --> 00:11:08.049
Do you want to get scolded?

00:11:23.541 --> 00:11:25.116
I'll go with you!

00:11:32.415 --> 00:11:34.036
What brings you here all of a sudden?

00:11:34.061 --> 00:11:36.133
I came to feel
the worth of creating 'It's You'.

00:11:36.134 --> 00:11:37.134
The worth?

00:11:37.210 --> 00:11:38.958
There's something like that.

00:11:39.283 --> 00:11:41.550
Let's just call it blind spot management.

00:11:48.298 --> 00:11:51.276
Deepfake crimes are becoming
more severe by the day

00:11:51.277 --> 00:11:53.946
and causing a huge social impact.

00:11:54.026 --> 00:11:58.672
Deepfake uses AI to manipulate
real people's face or specific part...

00:11:58.673 --> 00:12:00.489
Deepfakes are really convincing.

00:12:01.014 --> 00:12:02.441
People will be fooled by deepfakes.

00:12:02.666 --> 00:12:04.411
They say deepfakes are
used in stalking crimes too.

00:12:04.518 --> 00:12:08.202
Yeah. Like using the face of
someone you like or something?

00:12:08.222 --> 00:12:09.145
Yeah.

00:12:09.164 --> 00:12:11.013
People are out of their minds.

00:12:11.638 --> 00:12:15.787
Under the guise of love,
they cause great harm to others...

00:12:16.412 --> 00:12:19.200
Love? It's a crime!

00:12:19.231 --> 00:12:23.036
Advanced technology always has two sides.

00:12:23.361 --> 00:12:25.492
Is it the technology's fault?

00:12:25.511 --> 00:12:27.556
It's the people who misuse it.

00:12:27.727 --> 00:12:28.742
But

00:12:29.150 --> 00:12:32.479
isn't it similar to making
a prototype using Sunho as a model?

00:12:32.499 --> 00:12:33.614
Isn't it similar?

00:12:33.641 --> 00:12:34.511
C'mon.

00:12:34.530 --> 00:12:36.275
You can't say that, Manager!

00:12:36.295 --> 00:12:40.786
We take ethical and moral
considerations very seriously.

00:12:40.806 --> 00:12:44.235
And it was made with
Mr. Han's consent.

00:12:44.255 --> 00:12:45.255
That's right.

00:12:45.453 --> 00:12:47.925
That's also why we signed a big contract.

00:12:48.833 --> 00:12:49.912
[Sohee: Let's meet. Contact me.]

00:12:49.931 --> 00:12:51.836
But where is Jiyeon?

00:12:51.861 --> 00:12:52.855
I think Jiyeon went out for work.

00:12:52.856 --> 00:12:54.056
Don't contact me.

00:12:54.581 --> 00:12:55.581
San.

00:12:55.819 --> 00:12:56.360
Yes?

00:12:56.380 --> 00:12:57.936
By the way,

00:12:58.671 --> 00:13:03.556
if we can see 'ForMe', do you think
we'll be able to touch it someday?

00:13:07.639 --> 00:13:08.744
Don't you think so?

00:13:11.061 --> 00:13:12.129
[Sohee: No way. I like you.]

00:13:14.262 --> 00:13:15.296
No way.

00:13:15.351 --> 00:13:16.990
I like you.

00:13:19.841 --> 00:13:20.841
Who is it?

00:13:20.871 --> 00:13:22.096
Your girlfriend?

00:13:22.928 --> 00:13:24.088
It's not like that.

00:13:24.128 --> 00:13:24.851
C'mon.

00:13:24.870 --> 00:13:26.391
Why are you getting all shy?

00:13:26.411 --> 00:13:27.478
She is your girlfriend.

00:13:27.498 --> 00:13:29.528
I told you, it's not like that!

00:13:39.159 --> 00:13:40.446
I'm sorry.

00:13:42.232 --> 00:13:43.566
I'll get going now.

00:13:47.559 --> 00:13:49.433
[Yun Bia]

00:13:50.542 --> 00:13:51.542
Ah.

00:13:51.662 --> 00:13:53.787
So, you want to offer

00:13:53.806 --> 00:13:57.302
the 'ForMe Version 2' program
to our center?

00:13:57.322 --> 00:13:58.149
Yes.

00:13:59.131 --> 00:14:03.246
We're quite small,
so it might not get much publicity.

00:14:03.321 --> 00:14:06.250
Maybe you should try a bigger center...

00:14:06.270 --> 00:14:08.576
Actually, doing it
in a small place

00:14:08.595 --> 00:14:11.253
is much better for
the company's image.

00:14:11.548 --> 00:14:14.880
It doesn't look like blatant advertising,
it's more natural.

00:14:18.996 --> 00:14:20.766
Director is at it again.

00:14:21.081 --> 00:14:22.239
It's not just about promoting 'ForMe',

00:14:22.259 --> 00:14:25.526
Director Yun wants people
who really need 'ForMe' to use it.

00:14:26.996 --> 00:14:28.291
Is that so?

00:14:28.570 --> 00:14:32.102
Actually, everyone here feels lonely.

00:14:32.121 --> 00:14:34.606
They all want someone by their side.

00:14:38.898 --> 00:14:40.696
Then 'ForMe' is perfect for here.

00:14:41.744 --> 00:14:43.017
Sounds good.

00:14:43.018 --> 00:14:46.456
Since you're here,
would you like to meet the seniors?

00:14:46.475 --> 00:14:48.850
- That's okay...
- Sure, why not.

00:14:48.885 --> 00:14:50.210
Could you show us around?

00:15:02.178 --> 00:15:03.596
I said I don't want to!

00:15:07.051 --> 00:15:09.484
Please stop contacting me!

00:15:11.064 --> 00:15:12.064
What?

00:15:12.306 --> 00:15:13.306
Right now?

00:15:18.609 --> 00:15:19.609
Got it.

00:15:42.787 --> 00:15:43.986
Wow!

00:15:44.909 --> 00:15:46.163
Woah.

00:16:01.086 --> 00:16:03.086
Director Yun hasn't come back yet?

00:16:04.061 --> 00:16:04.910
No.

00:16:05.351 --> 00:16:07.979
Maybe Director Yun went straight home
after the fieldwork?

00:16:12.317 --> 00:16:13.191
Yes.

00:16:16.534 --> 00:16:19.165
Did Mr. Han go with him?

00:16:19.605 --> 00:16:20.655
I don't know.

00:16:20.675 --> 00:16:21.955
He didn't even reply to my text.

00:16:24.710 --> 00:16:25.566
Ugh.

00:16:25.585 --> 00:16:28.576
I'm really craving beer today!

00:16:30.511 --> 00:16:32.816
Anyone want to grab a beer with me?

00:16:41.274 --> 00:16:42.966
Here you are!

00:16:44.701 --> 00:16:46.046
Really?

00:16:47.746 --> 00:16:49.166
Meet me on the first floor.

00:16:49.491 --> 00:16:50.586
Hurry up.

00:16:52.750 --> 00:16:54.890
I'm heading out now.

00:16:54.891 --> 00:16:55.599
Great work, Yukyung.

00:16:55.619 --> 00:16:56.527
Thanks!

00:16:57.028 --> 00:16:57.902
I mean...

00:16:58.126 --> 00:16:59.851
I can say it...

00:16:59.871 --> 00:17:00.918
When should I say it?

00:17:00.938 --> 00:17:01.976
Next year?

00:17:02.107 --> 00:17:03.078
Ah!

00:17:03.097 --> 00:17:04.331
In the next life?

00:17:04.786 --> 00:17:05.786
Come with us, Song.

00:17:05.946 --> 00:17:07.191
What? Why me?

00:17:07.211 --> 00:17:08.505
How can I talk to Yukyung alone?

00:17:08.525 --> 00:17:10.676
Are we going to confess together?

00:17:12.234 --> 00:17:13.234
Hurry up, Song.

00:17:13.311 --> 00:17:14.311
Oh my!

00:17:14.933 --> 00:17:15.933
Goodness.

00:17:16.363 --> 00:17:18.415
Director Sul, we're heading out first.

00:17:18.559 --> 00:17:19.623
Thanks for your hard work.

00:17:19.643 --> 00:17:20.930
You too, great job.

00:17:21.733 --> 00:17:22.499
Come on, hurry.

00:17:22.519 --> 00:17:23.721
Let go of me.

00:17:23.760 --> 00:17:24.849
Help me out here.

00:17:24.850 --> 00:17:26.661
Help with what?
Do it yourself.

00:17:26.662 --> 00:17:27.735
You're my sister, Song.

00:17:28.216 --> 00:17:30.026
- Do I have to do everything for you?
- Yes.

00:17:33.868 --> 00:17:35.096
Aren't you cold?

00:17:35.471 --> 00:17:36.896
Let's take the car.

00:17:37.466 --> 00:17:38.761
I like walking.

00:17:38.856 --> 00:17:40.731
If you're cold, go ahead, Han Sunho.

00:17:40.751 --> 00:17:43.097
Looking for an unchanging love?

