00:34:41.765 --> 00:34:43.212
No, it's okay.

00:34:44.209 --> 00:34:45.780
It's not your fault, Jooyeon.

00:34:46.421 --> 00:34:47.391
Right.

00:34:47.411 --> 00:34:51.042
If Jooyeon had known about this,
she would have told us earlier.

00:34:52.274 --> 00:34:53.366
Are you sure it's not your fault?

00:34:54.006 --> 00:34:54.741
Jooyeon?

00:34:56.395 --> 00:34:58.096
Let's handle this first.

00:34:58.884 --> 00:34:59.884
Everyone,

00:35:00.291 --> 00:35:03.016
please make sure
this doesn't leak outside.

00:35:03.469 --> 00:35:04.469
- Okay.
- Okay.

00:35:05.879 --> 00:35:08.146
Please keep it quiet on your side too.

00:35:11.560 --> 00:35:12.560
Okay.

00:35:30.907 --> 00:35:31.982
Are you okay?

00:35:33.429 --> 00:35:34.429
Yeah.

00:35:35.514 --> 00:35:36.767
Are you upset?

00:35:38.730 --> 00:35:40.796
Well, I'm fine.

00:35:41.698 --> 00:35:43.226
It won't be a big deal.

00:35:43.401 --> 00:35:46.069
We'll permanently ban all related users

00:35:46.094 --> 00:35:48.626
and hold that woman legally responsible.

00:35:50.501 --> 00:35:52.435
And as for San...

00:35:52.455 --> 00:35:53.716
Forget about San.

00:35:54.831 --> 00:35:56.830
San didn't know about it either.

00:35:56.831 --> 00:35:58.186
How do you know that?

00:35:58.581 --> 00:36:00.606
How much do we really know about him?

00:36:00.785 --> 00:36:03.636
San has no reason to do that.

00:36:05.333 --> 00:36:07.508
You know I have
the authority to hire and fire, right?

00:36:08.131 --> 00:36:10.516
If you can't do it, I will.

00:36:10.586 --> 00:36:11.781
Are you going to fire San?

00:36:12.036 --> 00:36:13.745
Isn't he a valuable employee to you?

00:36:13.746 --> 00:36:17.761
Because he's valuable to 'It's You',
not just because he's San.

00:36:18.876 --> 00:36:20.841
I only need to protect 'It's You'.

00:36:21.286 --> 00:36:23.796
Anything that hinders
'It's You' must be cut off.

00:36:30.258 --> 00:36:34.496
If you're really set on that,
let's just suspend San for now.

00:36:35.011 --> 00:36:38.516
It's hard to find a talented developer
like San right away.

00:36:39.671 --> 00:36:43.306
This incident will make
San more cautious in the future.

00:36:46.722 --> 00:36:47.803
Alright.

00:36:48.424 --> 00:36:49.526
I understand.

00:36:50.581 --> 00:36:54.630
But if this happens again,

00:36:55.998 --> 00:36:57.455
you'll let me handle it my way.

00:37:00.882 --> 00:37:02.796
Yeah, I will.

00:37:07.687 --> 00:37:09.248
Go home early today.

00:37:09.551 --> 00:37:10.796
You look tired.

00:37:27.581 --> 00:37:29.261
Do you have any business
with Director Yun?

00:37:31.257 --> 00:37:32.272
No, I don't.

00:37:47.246 --> 00:37:48.536
Let's go home too.

00:37:53.451 --> 00:37:55.211
Or you could check out
Director Yun's office.

00:38:00.779 --> 00:38:02.916
You go ahead today.

00:38:06.228 --> 00:38:07.361
You go home first.

00:38:07.612 --> 00:38:08.612
Aren't you going home?

00:38:08.951 --> 00:38:10.596
I need to stay with Director Yun.

00:38:13.061 --> 00:38:13.831
Do you...

00:38:14.526 --> 00:38:16.126
really like Director Yun?

00:38:16.151 --> 00:38:16.746
Yeah.

00:38:16.765 --> 00:38:17.622
Yeah?

00:38:18.070 --> 00:38:19.009
Since when did you like Director Yun?

00:38:19.593 --> 00:38:20.515
Since when?

00:38:22.321 --> 00:38:23.321
Not sure...

00:38:26.939 --> 00:38:27.939
Why?

00:38:28.156 --> 00:38:29.156
What?

00:38:29.938 --> 00:38:32.146
Does Director Yun like you too?

00:38:33.003 --> 00:38:34.331
Does that matter?

00:38:34.456 --> 00:38:36.171
Of course it matters, why wouldn't it?

00:38:36.842 --> 00:38:38.597
Otherwise, you'll get hurt.

00:38:40.053 --> 00:38:41.834
If I was afraid of getting hurt,

00:38:41.861 --> 00:38:43.913
I would not have started
crushing on Director Yun.

00:38:52.812 --> 00:38:54.056
I'm heading home first.

00:38:54.220 --> 00:38:55.220
Okay.

00:39:07.274 --> 00:39:08.766
When did I start liking Director Yun?

00:39:12.884 --> 00:39:14.460
I told you to go home first.

00:39:14.479 --> 00:39:16.246
You never listen.

00:39:17.537 --> 00:39:19.092
How can I go home alone?

00:39:19.211 --> 00:39:20.276
I worry about you.

00:39:20.590 --> 00:39:21.789
Why are you worried about me?

00:39:21.790 --> 00:39:23.105
I'm not a kid.

00:39:24.272 --> 00:39:25.472
You're upset, aren't you?

00:39:28.225 --> 00:39:30.126
Yeah, I'm a bit upset.

00:39:31.294 --> 00:39:32.595
But...

00:39:32.878 --> 00:39:34.466
I'm trying to understand.

00:39:35.641 --> 00:39:37.924
It's just a mistake by someone,

00:39:38.420 --> 00:39:40.416
who didn't give up on love.

00:39:52.001 --> 00:39:54.836
In a world that was
created to not be lonely,

00:39:55.761 --> 00:39:58.156
why do people feel even lonelier?

00:39:59.361 --> 00:40:01.369
People love because they're lonely,

00:40:02.094 --> 00:40:04.796
but they feel lonelier because of love.

00:40:07.451 --> 00:40:08.451
Why?

00:40:09.451 --> 00:40:11.861
Maybe loneliness loves love too.

00:40:14.386 --> 00:40:16.586
You'll do well.

00:40:16.686 --> 00:40:18.376
How do you know that?

00:40:20.551 --> 00:40:22.116
Because I'll be by your side.

00:40:22.871 --> 00:40:25.391
Don't make promises you can't keep.

00:40:26.016 --> 00:40:27.271
Can I keep this one?

00:40:28.366 --> 00:40:29.651
Will you let me?

00:40:43.545 --> 00:40:44.831
Don't get out of the car.

00:40:45.381 --> 00:40:46.381
See you tomorrow.

00:40:50.751 --> 00:40:52.306
I'll walk you to your door.

00:40:53.771 --> 00:40:57.411
You always have to do what you want,
don't you?

00:40:57.836 --> 00:40:58.991
That's just how I am.

00:40:59.246 --> 00:41:01.051
I have to say everything I want to say.

00:41:08.971 --> 00:41:12.367
How can you be so sure
you'll stay by my side?

00:41:13.191 --> 00:41:15.995
I told you, everything is a choice.

00:41:16.820 --> 00:41:19.606
I've decided to stay by
this person no matter what.

00:41:20.501 --> 00:41:22.326
That's the choice I've made.

00:41:25.096 --> 00:41:27.406
What if you suddenly die tomorrow, Sunho?

00:41:29.077 --> 00:41:30.648
Then...

00:41:31.173 --> 00:41:33.452
I'll wander as a ghost

00:41:33.895 --> 00:41:35.566
and stay by your side, Bia.

00:41:35.961 --> 00:41:37.115
Is that supposed to be...

00:41:37.746 --> 00:41:39.436
romantic?

00:41:41.044 --> 00:41:42.896
But why kill me off suddenly?

00:41:43.251 --> 00:41:44.996
I'm going to live longer than anyone.

00:41:46.231 --> 00:41:48.666
Yes, live a long, long life, Sunho.

00:41:59.924 --> 00:42:01.050
I promise you.

00:42:03.851 --> 00:42:05.505
Even if the whole world
turns its back on you,

00:42:06.451 --> 00:42:07.772
I'll be by your side.

00:42:22.346 --> 00:42:24.008
When you feel alone,

00:42:24.633 --> 00:42:26.376
when there's nothing in front of you,

00:42:27.901 --> 00:42:28.976
look beside you.

00:42:30.731 --> 00:42:32.196
I'll be there.

00:42:41.722 --> 00:42:43.922
You hugged that girl earlier,
and now you're hugging me?

00:42:44.430 --> 00:42:47.438
Do you go around
hugging people often?

00:42:49.540 --> 00:42:50.615
Are you jealous?

00:42:52.169 --> 00:42:53.288
Am I jealous?

00:42:53.413 --> 00:42:54.466
No way.

00:42:58.339 --> 00:42:59.866
You should go home now.

00:43:02.290 --> 00:43:03.290
Goodnight.

00:43:03.690 --> 00:43:04.696
Just go.

00:43:23.838 --> 00:43:24.856
Who's there?

00:43:29.483 --> 00:43:30.893
Who is that?

00:43:30.913 --> 00:43:32.142
Oh my gosh.

00:43:32.367 --> 00:43:33.750
- Are you okay?
- Yeah.

00:43:33.751 --> 00:43:34.751
Jooyeon?

00:43:49.040 --> 00:43:50.040
What do you want from me?

00:43:51.601 --> 00:43:52.836
I'm sorry.

00:43:53.791 --> 00:43:55.476
I can't do this anymore.

00:44:00.592 --> 00:44:04.946
Is it really that hard to
separate Sunho from Bia?

00:44:05.471 --> 00:44:07.386
Please stop, Director Sul.

00:44:08.526 --> 00:44:09.526
Stop what?

00:44:09.761 --> 00:44:12.966
Why are you going this far, huh?

00:44:14.025 --> 00:44:15.631
Fine, I'll stop.

00:44:16.206 --> 00:44:17.851
Stop liking Bia.

00:44:20.426 --> 00:44:21.831
You like Bia, right?

00:44:23.611 --> 00:44:24.686
Wait, no.

00:44:26.301 --> 00:44:27.806
You love her, right?

00:44:28.701 --> 00:44:30.926
It's really disgusting...

00:44:31.852 --> 00:44:34.425
Do you think that's my weakness?

00:44:34.426 --> 00:44:35.426
Isn't it your weakness?

00:44:35.676 --> 00:44:37.514
You're afraid I'll do something to Bia,

00:44:37.515 --> 00:44:39.541
so you can't leave and do as I say.

00:44:43.174 --> 00:44:44.246
Mina!

00:44:46.529 --> 00:44:48.116
I'll pick you up in the morning.

00:44:55.914 --> 00:45:00.077
"If you don't want to die,
stay away from Yun Bia."

00:45:02.081 --> 00:45:03.207
Seriously,

00:45:03.632 --> 00:45:08.334
you can't even do the simple task
of separating Sunho from Bia!

00:45:09.131 --> 00:45:12.566
If you stay at the company,
who knows what I'll do next.

00:45:12.801 --> 00:45:14.846
You're useless now, so get lost!

00:45:28.197 --> 00:45:29.806
[Jooyeon]

00:45:31.573 --> 00:45:32.636
What is this?

00:45:40.548 --> 00:45:41.746
This is Hong Jooyeon.

00:45:42.381 --> 00:45:45.546
I have something to tell you
at the office tomorrow.

00:46:10.687 --> 00:46:13.249
[I'm exposing the two-faced nature of
employee Hong Jooyeon from 'It's You'.]

00:46:13.269 --> 00:46:14.409
[Her expression
suddenly shifted...]

00:46:14.429 --> 00:46:15.645
[And she asked: "Don't you want
to get closer to 'ForMe'?]

00:46:17.466 --> 00:46:19.008
[After telling me to cause
a scene, she played innocent]

00:46:19.028 --> 00:46:19.721
[Dummy]

00:46:19.741 --> 00:46:20.456
[Blackmail]

00:46:25.614 --> 00:46:27.156
Is Jooyeon really the culprit?

00:46:27.157 --> 00:46:28.396
Jooyeon wouldn't do that.

00:46:28.421 --> 00:46:30.889
Didn't Jooyeon really like Director Yun?

00:46:30.890 --> 00:46:34.046
Why not just ask Jooyeon directly?

00:46:34.066 --> 00:46:34.890
Of course.

00:46:34.910 --> 00:46:36.786
This must be a misunderstanding...

00:46:40.362 --> 00:46:41.496
Jooyeon.

00:46:44.063 --> 00:46:45.328
It's not like that...

00:46:54.927 --> 00:46:56.952
Director Yun, it's not like that.

00:46:59.151 --> 00:47:00.756
Hey, Sul Jaehee!

00:47:03.657 --> 00:47:05.251
I didn't do it.

00:47:05.261 --> 00:47:07.666
Then why was all this with Jooyeon?

00:47:08.961 --> 00:47:10.806
Because Jooyeon did it.

00:47:14.912 --> 00:47:16.271
I didn't do it.

00:47:17.196 --> 00:47:18.891
It wasn't me!

00:47:19.746 --> 00:47:22.231
I'm telling you, it wasn't me!

00:47:23.606 --> 00:47:26.111
Director Yun, it wasn't me.

00:47:26.331 --> 00:47:27.780
Please believe me, okay?

00:47:27.918 --> 00:47:28.998
I didn't do it.

00:47:29.018 --> 00:47:30.122
Then who?

00:47:31.031 --> 00:47:32.376
Who did it then?

00:47:41.587 --> 00:47:42.696
Get out of here right now.

00:47:43.831 --> 00:47:44.831
I don't want to leave.

00:47:46.411 --> 00:47:48.316
Do you want to be dragged out by security?

00:47:51.650 --> 00:47:53.081
You'll regret this.

00:47:53.706 --> 00:47:54.706
Who will regret it?

00:47:56.087 --> 00:47:57.087
Me?

00:48:11.566 --> 00:48:12.581
Sul Jaehee.

00:48:13.906 --> 00:48:15.446
Can we talk for a moment?

00:48:22.332 --> 00:48:25.427
Did you really have to go that far
with Jooyeon in front of everyone?

00:48:25.447 --> 00:48:26.966
What should I have done then?

00:48:27.841 --> 00:48:30.267
Jooyeon messed with the server
and even threatened you,

00:48:30.268 --> 00:48:31.627
trying to ruin the company!

00:48:31.647 --> 00:48:33.856
You could've heard why she did it.

00:48:34.095 --> 00:48:35.095
Why?

00:48:35.231 --> 00:48:36.636
Are you curious about that?

00:48:37.351 --> 00:48:38.586
Is that important to you?

00:48:39.041 --> 00:48:41.446
Since when were
those things important to us?

00:48:41.801 --> 00:48:43.659
What's important is...

00:48:44.012 --> 00:48:45.786
protecting the company together.

00:48:46.221 --> 00:48:47.221
Isn't that right?

00:48:49.161 --> 00:48:50.276
That's right.

00:48:51.471 --> 00:48:52.798
And that includes...

00:48:54.014 --> 00:48:55.653
the employees too.

00:49:05.191 --> 00:49:07.021
What's going on here?

00:49:07.633 --> 00:49:09.400
The dummy was shocking enough,

00:49:10.152 --> 00:49:11.400
but to think...

00:49:12.003 --> 00:49:14.056
it was all Jooyeon's doing...

00:49:14.321 --> 00:49:15.816
Why would Jooyeon do that?

00:49:16.351 --> 00:49:18.387
Does she have a grudge
against our company

00:49:18.561 --> 00:49:19.976
or something?

00:49:21.681 --> 00:49:23.055
But Director Sul

00:49:23.074 --> 00:49:25.396
is colder than I thought.

00:49:26.161 --> 00:49:27.916
It's a matter concerning the company.

00:49:30.451 --> 00:49:32.996
Still, Director Sul was quite ruthless.

00:49:39.622 --> 00:49:40.548
Wow...

00:49:40.567 --> 00:49:41.816
It's starting now.

00:49:42.711 --> 00:49:44.856
Everyone, unplug your phones.

00:50:01.706 --> 00:50:03.996
What brings you here?

00:50:05.291 --> 00:50:09.076
I'm here to see the Director.

00:50:09.852 --> 00:50:12.760
If it's about that issue,

00:50:12.779 --> 00:50:15.758
we're planning to release
an official statement soon,

00:50:15.778 --> 00:50:17.396
so please wait a little...

00:50:17.595 --> 00:50:18.880
I'm here to see...

00:50:19.415 --> 00:50:20.949
my daughter.

00:50:21.041 --> 00:50:22.041
Your daughter.

00:50:24.317 --> 00:50:25.317
Your daughter?

00:50:26.752 --> 00:50:27.766
Did you forget?

00:50:29.021 --> 00:50:31.249
Why did we created 'ForMe'?

00:50:31.604 --> 00:50:34.371
Why we're we trapped in that dark room?

00:50:34.696 --> 00:50:35.886
Jaehee...

00:50:36.236 --> 00:50:37.926
We're different now
than we were back then.

00:50:37.946 --> 00:50:38.860
What?

00:50:39.468 --> 00:50:40.972
How are we different?

00:50:41.997 --> 00:50:43.811
Is it because Han Sunho is by your side?

00:50:44.481 --> 00:50:47.596
So you can go anywhere freely
without time constraints?

00:50:54.063 --> 00:50:55.582
Yun Bia, get a grip.

00:50:56.607 --> 00:50:59.134
People are pointing fingers at you,
the one who killed your parents,

00:50:59.659 --> 00:51:03.216
at your relatives who split
your parents' life insurance money,

00:51:03.727 --> 00:51:07.921
your teachers and classmates who gossiped
and exaggerated like Gossip Girl.

00:51:08.443 --> 00:51:10.045
And at your dying father,

00:51:10.046 --> 00:51:13.666
at your mother who abandoned you and
had an affair with another man.

00:51:15.044 --> 00:51:17.876
You hated and resented people.

00:51:18.691 --> 00:51:21.936
You were the one who said
you'd never trust in people or love!

00:51:22.084 --> 00:51:23.486
Just the two of us...

00:51:25.386 --> 00:51:28.236
can't live trapped
in that time forever.

00:51:31.671 --> 00:51:33.710
I don't want to live like that anymore.

00:51:42.276 --> 00:51:44.328
Even if you get hurt again?

00:51:47.153 --> 00:51:48.736
Are you really okay with that?

00:51:52.086 --> 00:51:54.850
So please tell me your daughter's name.

00:51:54.870 --> 00:51:55.832
No.

00:51:55.851 --> 00:51:57.880
Let me just find my daughter.

00:51:57.881 --> 00:51:59.668
- Are you sure you're in right department?
- No.

00:51:59.688 --> 00:52:02.757
Excuse me, my daughter...

00:52:02.758 --> 00:52:05.419
Ma'am, where are you looking for, okay?

00:52:05.420 --> 00:52:06.810
Please check if my daughter is here.

00:52:06.990 --> 00:52:09.211
What's your daughter's name?

00:52:09.232 --> 00:52:10.210
You can't do this here.

00:52:10.210 --> 00:52:10.823
Auntie...

00:52:10.824 --> 00:52:11.878
My daughter said she was here...

00:52:11.879 --> 00:52:13.756
What's your daughter's name?

00:52:14.181 --> 00:52:15.600
You can't do this here.

00:52:15.601 --> 00:52:17.076
Please find my daughter.

00:52:26.117 --> 00:52:27.156
Mom...

00:52:29.341 --> 00:52:30.526
Here you are.

00:52:31.941 --> 00:52:33.206
My beautiful daughter.

00:52:52.773 --> 00:52:55.506
I came all the way here
because I missed you.